[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0955","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0955.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1112","title":"IrfanView IrfanView32 图片文件缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"IrfanView32 3.0.7 及更早版本在处理 Photoshop 图片文件头时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，当文件头中\"8BPS\"图像类型后跟随超长字符串时，触发栈缓冲区溢出。攻击者可构造特制的 .psd 图片文件，诱使用户在 IrfanView32 中打开，从而在目标系统上执行任意命令。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1112"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-09T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:44.740","remediation":"升级 IrfanView 至最新版本（当前最新版为 4.6x 系列，已修复此缓冲区溢出漏洞）。临时缓解措施：避免打开来源不明的 Photoshop PSD 图像文件，可在文件资源管理器中取消 .psd 文件与 IrfanView 的默认关联。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://stud4.tuwien.ac.at/~e9227474/main2.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/34066","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/781","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3549","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19610","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1112.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1112","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1112.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1112.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1112.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/979579ffd61606c64cf772a1e865f5126788e4ec/1999.tsv","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/781/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1112.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000869.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0955.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0954","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0954.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0639","title":"Unix Chargen 服务反射放大拒绝服务漏洞","description":"chargen（字符生成）服务是一种过时的网络诊断协议，默认监听 TCP/UDP 19 端口，在接收到连接请求后会持续输出大量字符数据。攻击者可通过伪造源 IP 地址向目标系统的 UDP chargen 服务发送小数据包，利用服务放大响应流量实施分布式拒绝服务（DDoS）攻击。此外，该服务无需认证即可访问，可能导致信息泄露和服务滥用。该问题属于安全配置缺陷，影响 Unix/Linux 及部分 Windows 系统中默认启用 inetd 的版本。修复措施为在 inetd 配置中禁用 chargen 服务（注释掉 /etc/inetd.conf 中相关行）或使用防火墙阻止外部对 19 端口的访问。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0639"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:46.383","remediation":"在 Unix/Linux 系统中，编辑 /etc/inetd.conf 文件，注释或删除 chargen 相关行（如 chargen stream tcp nowait root internal），然后重启 inetd 服务（`kill -HUP <inetd_pid>`）。在 Windows 系统中，通过「服务」管理器禁用 \"Simple TCP/IP Services\" 或 \"Character Generator\" 服务。该服务为过时诊断协议，无业务依赖时应彻底禁用，防止被用于 UDP/TCP 反射放大攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0639","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0639.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0639.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0639","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0639.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0639.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0639.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0639.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83127/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0954.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0953","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0953.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1111","title":"Immunix StackGuard 缓冲区溢出安全绕过漏洞","description":"StackGuard（GCC 编译器缓冲区溢出保护扩展）1.21 之前版本存在安全机制绕过漏洞。攻击者可通过非线性攻击方式直接修改指向返回地址的指针，绕过 Random Canary 和 Terminator Canary 等栈保护机制，而非通过传统缓冲区溢出覆盖返回地址条目本身。该漏洞使得基于 Canary 的栈保护失效，远程攻击者在无需触发 Canary 检测的情况下即可实施缓冲区溢出攻击，严重威胁系统安全。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1111"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-09T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:44.603","remediation":"立即升级 StackGuard 至 1.21 或更高版本，该版本引入了 XOR Random Canary 保护机制，将 canary 值与返回地址进行异或绑定，有效防御绕过随机 canary 和终止符 canary 的非线性指针攻击。如无法立即升级，应审查代码中是否存在通过缓冲区溢出修改指针变量后指向返回地址的攻击面，避免使用 gets() 等不安全的字符串输入函数。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94218618329838&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/786","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3524","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1111.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1111","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1111.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1111.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1111.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fpjr-9gj6-mc3v/GHSA-fpjr-9gj6-mc3v.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1111.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idbypass","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--5fd10034-0e95-458a-8e9d-f6ddb2de6532.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0953.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0951","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0951.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1110","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5 Media Player ActiveX 文件存在性信息泄露漏洞","description":"Windows Media Player ActiveX 控件在 Internet Explorer 5.0 中被调用时，当指定文件不存在会返回特定错误码，导致存在信息泄露漏洞。远程攻击者可构造恶意网页，通过脚本调用该 ActiveX 对象并捕获返回的错误信息，从而探测目标系统上任意文件是否存在，威胁用户隐私安全。该漏洞仅影响安装了 Windows Media Player 的 Internet Explorer 5 用户。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1110"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-14T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:44.477","remediation":"升级 Internet Explorer 至 5.01 Service Pack 2 以上版本，或安装 Microsoft 安全更新 MS00-009 对应补丁。如无法升级，在注册表 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Internet Explorer\\ActiveX Compatibility 中为 Windows Media Player ActiveX 控件 CLSID 设置兼容性标志 (Flags=0x400) 以禁用 Kill Bit，阻止其在 IE 中加载。同时建议将 IE 升级至 6.0 及以上版本以彻底消除该风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/34675","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/793","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19618","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1110.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1110.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1110","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1110.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1110.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1110.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mhq8-h8mw-8cgr/GHSA-mhq8-h8mw-8cgr.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1110.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000876.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0951.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0951.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0951.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0949","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0949.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1109","title":"Eric Allman Sendmail 8.10.0 ETRN命令处理拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Sendmail 8.10.0 之前版本中存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标 SMTP 服务器发送大量 ETRN 命令后立即断开连接来触发该漏洞。当攻击者断开连接后，Sendmail 进程仍会继续处理已接收的 ETRN 命令，持续消耗服务器资源，导致邮件服务响应缓慢甚至崩溃，影响正常邮件收发功能。该漏洞利用简单，无需认证，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1109"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-22T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:44.347","remediation":"升级 Sendmail 至 8.10.0 或更高版本，该版本修复了 ETRN 命令处理中连接断开后继续处理导致资源耗尽的问题。如无法升级，可在 sendmail.cf 中限制 ETRN 命令来源 IP，或通过防火墙限制 SMTP 端口入站连接频次作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94632241202626&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94780566911948&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7760.php","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/904","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19701","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1109.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1109","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1109.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1109.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1109.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jw39-vxm9-j3xr/GHSA-jw39-vxm9-j3xr.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/sendmail_etrn_dos.nasl","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000955.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1109.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0949.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0948","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0948.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0636","title":"多厂商 Discard 服务安全配置漏洞","description":"Discard 服务（RFC 863，TCP/UDP 端口 9）是一种诊断网络服务，收到所有数据后直接丢弃而不做任何处理。该服务在生产环境中启用会无谓增加系统攻击面，攻击者可通过端口扫描发现该服务并确认主机存活，用于网络侦察；在 UDP 模式下，还可被用于反射放大 DDoS 攻击的流量放大链，导致目标网络带宽耗尽。此外，大量向该服务发送数据包可能造成服务器资源消耗。该漏洞无需认证、可远程利用，影响所有启用了 discard 服务的系统，应关闭该服务或通过防火墙限制访问。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0636"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:46.037","remediation":"在 Linux/Unix 中编辑 /etc/inetd.conf 注释 discard 相关行（stream 和 dgram）并重启 inetd 服务；systemd 系统执行 systemctl mask discard.socket 停止并屏蔽 discard socket。Windows 系统通过控制面板取消勾选\"简单 TCP/IP 服务\"或运行 dism /online /disable-feature /featurename:SimpleTCP 卸载。同时建议在防火墙上阻断 TCP 和 UDP 端口 9 的入站流量，并检查禁用 echo（端口 7）、chargen（端口 19）等类似高危服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0636","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0636.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0636","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0636.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0636.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0636.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/SHN_discard.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0636.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83127/info.html","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--78c74f51-06af-4c13-a78e-77284614fcad.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0948.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0947","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0947.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1105","title":"Microsoft Windows 95 远程任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Windows 95 在启用 NetWare 网络的远程管理和文件共享功能时存在设计缺陷，当管理员远程登录系统后会自动创建隐藏的 C$ 共享目录，且未对共享访问权限进行有效限制。远程攻击者无需高级权限，只需通过网络映射该驱动器即可读取目标系统上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Windows 95 操作系统，利用方式简单，危害主要为信息泄露。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1105"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:43.947","remediation":"立即禁用 Remote Administration 和 File Sharing for NetWare Networks 功能（进入控制面板 → 网络 → 服务，移除 File and Printer Sharing for NetWare Networks 及相关绑定）。由于 Windows 95 已终止支持，建议尽快迁移至受支持的 Windows 10/11 或 Windows Server 版本，并确保 SMB 服务不暴露于公网。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7231.php","http://www.net-security.sk/bugs/NT/netware1.html","http://www.zdnet.com/eweek/reviews/1016/tr42bug.html","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1105.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1105.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1105.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1105.json","https://github.com/0xMarcio/cve/blob/8fb60f1e10e801132244052aaca5ef57fba4fd01/1999/CVE-1999-1105.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rcfw-38c9-2wm8/GHSA-rcfw-38c9-2wm8.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1105","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88095/info.html","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1105.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1105.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0947.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0946","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0946.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0635","title":"多种操作系统 Echo 服务运行反射放大拒绝服务漏洞","description":"回声服务（Echo Service）运行于 TCP/UDP 端口 7，该服务将接收到的任意数据原样返回给发送方。攻击者可利用此服务进行信息收集，探测目标系统存活状态；更严重的是，攻击者可伪造源地址利用 UDP 回声服务发起反射放大型拒绝服务攻击，大量响应数据包会涌向被伪造的目标地址，导致目标带宽或资源耗尽。该漏洞影响默认开启该服务的所有旧版本操作系统。修复建议为禁用回声服务或通过防火墙阻止外部对端口 7 的访问。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0635"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:45.917","remediation":"立即禁用回声服务（echo service）：在 Unix/Linux 系统中注释 `/etc/inetd.conf` 中的 echo 行并重启 inetd，或执行 `systemctl disable echo-dgram echo-stream` 禁用 systemd socket；在 Windows 系统中通过服务管理器停止并禁用 Simple TCP/IP Services 或使用 `sc stop echo` 命令。同时在边界防火墙上封禁 UDP/TCP 7 端口以防止反射放大攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://lists.grok.org.uk/pipermail/full-disclosure/2006-January/041434.html","http://secunia.com/advisories/18514","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0635.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0635.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0635","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0635.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0635.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0635.md","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/echo.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0635.json","https://github.com/entrysky/mageni/blob/c58dcc9bc43b7fb267bb10a8083ada356fbc81d1/plugins/2009/echo_udp.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0946.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0945","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0945.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0634","title":"SSH 服务运行配置暴露","description":"CVE-1999-0634 已被拒绝使用。该编号原用于描述\"SSH 服务正在运行\"这一配置状态，但经评估该条目并非直接引入安全漏洞的缺陷，而属于安全配置管理范畴。此类配置项更适合纳入通用配置枚举（CCE）体系进行管理，因此 CVE 编号委员会决定拒绝此编号。该问题不涉及具体的攻击方法、漏洞原理或影响范围。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0634"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.870","remediation":"评估 SSH 服务是否必需，非必需则关闭 sshd 服务（systemctl disable sshd）；如需保留，配置密钥认证登录、禁用 root 直接登录（PermitRootLogin no）、修改默认端口 22 为高编号端口、限制来源 IP（hosts.allow/iptables），并保持 OpenSSH 为最新稳定版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0634.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0634","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0634.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0634.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/lymwhen/lymwhen.github.io/blob/b77540924df6be1e7c614e34dd724374affd2cbf/Linux/%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D.md","https://github.com/athiasjerome/XORCISM/blob/327e2a3be196660f82c89ae9d7c4e7abe4785b0d/SOURCES/XProviderQualys/QualysSampleResults.xml","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/5c36feecacaa0eef96caef76eb433e2bf57c7235/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0634.json","https://github.com/thoraf20/vulnscan/blob/600477d061ab5462099630f9f0924cc5383c5452/network.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0945.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0944","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0944.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1104","title":"Microsoft Windows 95 密码列表文件弱加密权限提升漏洞","description":"Windows 95 在启用密码缓存时对密码列表（.pwl）文件使用弱加密算法进行存储，本地攻击者可通过直接访问该文件并利用加密缺陷破译其中的明文密码，从而获取系统登录凭据并提升自身权限。该漏洞影响所有启用密码缓存的 Windows 95 系统，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。微软已发布相关安全公告。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1104"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:43.830","remediation":"Windows 95 已停止支持且无官方安全更新。建议立即禁用密码缓存：打开控制面板 → 密码 → 更改密码 → 点击\"开始使用\"并取消勾选所有密码缓存选项，同时删除 %WINDIR% 目录下所有 .pwl 文件。作为根本解决方案，应升级至仍受支持的 Windows 版本（如 Windows 10/11）以消除此风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167418931&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=88536273725787&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=88540877601866&w=2","http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q140/5/57.asp","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/71.php","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1104.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1104.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1104","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1104.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1104.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wmcw-55j3-3jh6/GHSA-wmcw-55j3-3jh6.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1104.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000995.txt","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0944.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0943","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0943.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0633","title":"HTTP/WWW 服务运行配置检查项（非漏洞）","description":"CVE-1999-0633 已被官方驳回（REJECT），原候选编号指向\"HTTP/WWW 服务正在运行\"这一配置检测项。该条目涉及的是系统上 HTTP 服务端口的开放状态识别，并非安全漏洞，不具备攻击条件和利用方式，不产生 CVSS 评分。此类配置检查更适合归入通用配置枚举（CCE）体系，而非 CVE 漏洞编号体系。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0633"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.750","remediation":"若 HTTP 服务非业务必需，应在系统服务管理器中禁用 httpd/nginx/IIS 等相关服务并配置防火墙阻止 80/443 端口入站流量；若为业务必要，应确保移除默认页面、禁用目录列表、限制访问来源 IP、启用 TLS 并定期更新 Web 服务器至最新稳定版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0633.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0633","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0633.json","https://github.com/scipag/AttackToolKit/blob/78bf88564956b8f18a37659dc3d345093e95a136/plugins/HTTP%20index.html%20check.plugin","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0633.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000461.txt","https://github.com/lymwhen/lymwhen.github.io/blob/b77540924df6be1e7c614e34dd724374affd2cbf/Linux/%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D.md","https://github.com/Planet-Source-Code/marc-ruef-attack-tool-kit-4-0__1-58262/blob/47bd1012c1edf591e9c9fe874122b617137e1b87/atk-4.0src/plugins/HTTP%20404%20enumeration.plugin","https://github.com/zmerry/z-marvel.github.io/blob/581a79f0e7ceb8cdb3e444922154e004cca44bbb/vulbox/webvul/low/%E5%8F%AF%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87HTTP%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96%E8%BF%9C%E7%AB%AFWWW%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0943.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0942","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0942.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1102","title":"BSD lpr 本地任意文件写入漏洞","description":"BSD 系统中 lpr 打印服务组件存在任意文件写入漏洞，本地攻击者可通过符号链接（symlink）攻击方式，在多次调用 lpr 命令（约 1000 次）后触发竞争条件，导致以 lp 权限创建或覆盖系统任意文件。该漏洞影响 SunOS 4.1.1、BSD 4.3、A/UX 2.0.1 及其他基于 BSD 的操作系统，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1102"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:43.580","remediation":"建议升级至现代 BSD 发行版（FreeBSD 4.0+/OpenBSD 2.0+）或改用 CUPS 替代 lpr 打印系统。如因兼容性无法升级，可通过移除 lpr 的 setuid 权限作为临时缓解：`chmod u-s /usr/bin/lpr`，但会限制普通用户使用打印功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/e-25.shtml","http://www.aenigma.net/resources/maillist/bugtraq/1994/0091.htm","http://www.phreak.org/archives/security/8lgm/8lgm.lpr","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1102.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1102","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1102.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1102.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1102.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-97ch-49wx-wfmx/GHSA-97ch-49wx-wfmx.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88452/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000994.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1102.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0942.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0941","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0941.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1101","title":"Kabsoftware Lydia 弱加密存储漏洞","description":"Kabsoftware Lydia 工具使用弱加密算法将用户密码存储在 lydia.ini 配置文件中，本地攻击者可通过直接读取该配置文件并利用加密算法的弱点轻易解密出明文密码，从而获取系统提升权限。该漏洞属于本地提权类型，攻击者需要具有本地系统访问权限，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。建议厂商采用强加密算法存储敏感凭据。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1101"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-02-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:43.450","remediation":"由于该软件发行于 1999 年、厂商已停止维护，建议立即迁移至支持强加密（如 AES-256-GCM 或 bcrypt）的现代密码管理工具。如暂时无法替换，可通过文件系统 ACL 将 lydia.ini 的访问权限收紧为仅管理员可读（chmod 600 lydia.ini），同时对所在目录启用操作系统级加密（如 Windows EFS / BitLocker 或 Linux eCryptfs），限制本地低权限用户读取该文件，降低凭据泄露风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/12618","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1101.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1101","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1101.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1101.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1101.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fj6p-4jfw-5336/GHSA-fj6p-4jfw-5336.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88477/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/979579ffd61606c64cf772a1e865f5126788e4ec/1999.tsv","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1101.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000535.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0941.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0940","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0940.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1100","title":"Cisco PIX Private Link 配置文件加密漏洞","description":"Cisco PIX Private Link 4.1.6及更早版本在处理配置文件中的特定命令时存在加密强度削弱漏洞，导致 DES 密钥有效长度从标准 56 位降低至 48 位。攻击者可利用该弱点对加密通信实施暴力破解，从而获取敏感信息。该漏洞影响 Cisco PIX 防火墙设备的 Private Link 功能，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。厂商已发布安全公告并提供修复建议。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1100"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:43.327","remediation":"升级 Cisco PIX Private Link 至 4.2 及以上版本，其中已修复 DES 密钥处理逻辑，恢复完整密钥长度。如无法升级或产品已停服，应将加密方案迁移至 AES（如 IPsec 配置中改用 AES-128/256），弃用 DES 算法；同时在防火墙 ACL 中限制可访问 PIX Private Link 管理接口的源 IP 范围，减少暴力破解攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/i-056.shtml","http://www.cisco.com/warp/public/770/pixkey-pub.shtml","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1579","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1100.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1100.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1100","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1100.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1100.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1100.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mv5q-6rw5-rqwv/GHSA-mv5q-6rw5-rqwv.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1100.json","https://github.com/robinzixuan/attackmap/blob/3e50ba1e011308b7d6ea18a627132f0a357f36c0/Asia/bruteresult.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0940.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0939","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0939.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0632","title":"通用 RPC Portmapper 服务信息泄露漏洞","description":"系统运行了 RPC 端口映射服务（rpcbind），该服务会向远程查询者暴露主机上运行的所有 RPC 服务的程序号、版本号和端口号。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可利用该服务收集系统上运行的 RPC 服务清单，从而获取目标系统信息以辅助进一步攻击，构成信息泄露风险。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.3,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0632"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:45.710","remediation":"在网络边界防火墙上阻止 TCP/UDP 111 端口的入站流量，防止外部枚举 RPC 服务。如业务不需要 RPC 服务，可禁用 portmap/rpcbind 服务（Linux 上执行 `systemctl disable rpcbind && systemctl stop rpcbind`）；若需使用，应限制仅信任来源 IP 可访问，避免暴露在公网。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0632","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/